<item>
            <title>[LU-8189] osc_match_base prototype differs from declaration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8189</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Declared in lustre/osc/osc_request.c&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; osc_match_base(struct obd_export *exp, struct ldlm_res_id *res_id,
                   &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_type type, union ldlm_policy_data *policy,
                   &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;enum&lt;/span&gt; ldlm_mode mode, __u64 *flags, void *data,
                   struct lustre_handle *lockh, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; unref)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But prototype in lustre/osc/osc_internal.h is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; osc_match_base(struct obd_export *exp, struct ldlm_res_id *res_id,
                   __u32 type, union ldlm_policy_data *policy, __u32 mode,
                   __u64 *flags, void *data, struct lustre_handle *lockh,
                   &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; unref);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
